  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "田叔者，趙陘城人也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "其先，齊田氏苗裔也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "叔喜劍，學黃老術於樂巨公所。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "叔為人刻廉自喜，喜游諸公。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "趙人舉之趙相趙午，午言之趙王張敖所，趙王以為郎中。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "數歲，切直廉平，趙王賢之，未及遷。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "會陳豨反代，漢七年，高祖往誅之，過趙，趙王張敖自持案進食，禮恭甚，高祖箕踞罵之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "是時趙相趙午等數十人皆怒，謂張王曰：「王事上禮備矣，今遇王如是，臣等請為亂。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "」趙王齧指出血，曰：「先人失國，微陛下，臣等當蟲出。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "公等柰何言若是！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "毋復出口矣！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "」於是貫高等曰：「王長者，不倍德。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "」卒私相與謀弒上。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "會事發覺，漢下詔捕趙王及群臣反者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "於是趙午等皆自殺，唯貫高就系。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "是時漢下詔書：「趙有敢隨王者罪三族。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "」唯孟舒、田叔等十餘人赭衣自髡鉗，稱王家奴，隨趙王敖至長安。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "貫高事明白，趙王敖得出，廢為宣平侯，乃進言田叔等十餘人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "上盡召見，與語，漢廷臣毋能出其右者，上說，盡拜為郡守、諸侯相。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "叔為漢中守十餘年，會高后崩，諸呂作亂，大臣誅之，立孝文帝。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "孝文帝既立，召田叔問之曰：「公知天下長者乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "」對曰：「臣何足以知之！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "」上曰：「公，長者也，宜知之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "」叔頓首曰：「故雲中守孟舒，長者也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "」是時孟舒坐虜大入塞盜劫，雲中尤甚，免。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "上曰：「先帝置孟舒雲中十餘年矣，虜曾一人，孟舒不能堅守，毋故士卒戰死者數百人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "長者固殺人乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "公何以言孟舒為長者也？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "」叔叩頭對曰：「是乃孟舒所以為長者也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "夫貫高等謀反，上下明詔，趙有敢隨張王，罪三族。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "然孟舒自髡鉗，隨張王敖之所在，欲以身死之，豈自知為雲中守哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "漢與楚相距，士卒罷敝。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "匈奴冒頓新服北夷，來為邊害，孟舒知士卒罷敝，不忍出言，士爭臨城死敵，如子為父，弟為兄，以故死者數百人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "孟舒豈故驅戰之哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "是乃孟舒所以為長者也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "」於是上曰：「賢哉孟舒！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "」復召孟舒以為雲中守。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "後數歲，叔坐法失官。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "梁孝王使人殺故吳相袁盎，景帝召田叔案梁，具得其事，還報。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "景帝曰：「梁有之乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "」叔對曰：「死罪！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "有之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "」上曰：「其事安在？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "」田叔曰：「上毋以梁事為也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "」上曰：「何也？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "」曰：「今梁王不伏誅，是漢法不行也；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "如其伏法，而太后食不甘味，臥不安席，此憂在陛下也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "」景帝大賢之，以為魯相。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "魯相初到，民自言相，訟王取其財物百餘人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "田叔取其渠率二十人，各笞五十，餘各搏二十，怒之曰：「王非若主邪？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "何自敢言若主！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "」魯王聞之大慚，發中府錢，使相償之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "相曰：「王自奪之，使相償之，是王為惡而相為善也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "相毋與償之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "」於是王乃盡償之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "魯王好獵，相常從入苑中，王輒休相就館舍，相出，常暴坐待王苑外。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "王數使人請相休，終不休，曰：「我王暴露苑中，我獨何為就舍！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "」魯王以故不大出游。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "數年，叔以官卒，魯以百金祠，少子仁不受也，曰：「不以百金傷先人名。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "仁以壯健為衛將軍舍人，數從擊匈奴。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "衛將軍進言仁，仁為郎中。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "數歲，為二千石丞相長史，失官。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "其後使刺舉三河。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "上東巡，仁奏事有辭，上說，拜為京輔都尉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "月餘，上遷拜為司直。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "數歲，坐太子事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "時左相自將兵，令司直田仁主閉守城門，坐縱太子，下吏誅死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "仁發兵，長陵令車千秋上變仁，仁族死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "陘城今在中山國。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "太史公曰：孔子稱曰「居是國必聞其政」，田叔之謂乎！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "義不忘賢，明主之美以救過。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "仁與余善，余故并論之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "褚先生曰：臣為郎時，聞之曰田仁故與任安相善。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "任安，滎陽人也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "少孤貧困，為人將車之長安，留，求事為小吏，未有因緣也，因占著名數。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "武功，扶風西界小邑也，谷口蜀道近山。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "安以為武功小邑，無豪，易高也，安留，代人為求盜亭父。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "後為亭長。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "邑中人民俱出獵，任安常為人分麋鹿雉兔，部署老小當壯劇易處，眾人皆喜，曰：「無傷也，任少卿分別平，有智略。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "」明日復合會，會者數百人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "任少卿曰：「某子甲何為不來乎？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "」諸人皆怪其見之疾也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "其後除為三老，舉為親民，出為三百石長，治民。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0085",
          "zh": "坐上行出游共帳不辦，斥免。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0086",
          "zh": "乃為衛將軍舍人，與田仁會，俱為舍人，居門下，同心相愛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0087",
          "zh": "此二人家貧，無錢用以事將軍家監，家監使養惡齧馬。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0088",
          "zh": "兩人同床臥，仁竊言曰：「不知人哉家監也！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0089",
          "zh": "」任安曰：「將軍尚不知人，何乃家監也！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0090",
          "zh": "」衛將軍從此兩人過平陽主，主家令兩人與騎奴同席而食，此二子拔刀列斷席別坐。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0091",
          "zh": "主家皆怪而惡之，莫敢呵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0092",
          "zh": "其後有詔募擇衛將軍舍人以為郎，將軍取舍人中富給者，令具鞌馬絳衣玉具劍，欲入奏之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0093",
          "zh": "會賢大夫少府趙禹來過衛將軍，將軍呼所舉舍人以示趙禹。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0094",
          "zh": "趙禹以次問之，十餘人無一人習事有智略者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0095",
          "zh": "趙禹曰：「吾聞之，將門之下必有將類。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0096",
          "zh": "傳曰『不知其君視其所使，不知其子視其所友』。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0097",
          "zh": "今有詔舉將軍舍人者，欲以觀將軍而能得賢者文武之士也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0098",
          "zh": "今徒取盎人子上之，又無智略，如木偶人衣之綺繡耳，將柰之何？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0099",
          "zh": "」於是趙禹悉召衛將軍舍人百餘人，以次問之，得田仁、任安，曰：「獨此兩人可耳，餘無可用者。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0100",
          "zh": "」衛將軍見此兩人貧，意不平。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0101",
          "zh": "趙禹去，謂兩人曰：「各自具樾象絳衣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0102",
          "zh": "」兩人對曰：「家貧無用具也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0103",
          "zh": "」將軍怒曰：「今兩君家自為貧，何為出此言？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0104",
          "zh": "鞅鞅如有移德於我者，何也？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0105",
          "zh": "」將軍不得已，上籍以聞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0106",
          "zh": "有詔召見衛將軍舍人，此二人前見，詔問能略相推第也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0107",
          "zh": "田仁對曰；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0108",
          "zh": "「提桴鼓立軍門，使士大夫樂死戰鬬，仁不及任安。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0109",
          "zh": "」任安對曰：「夫決嫌疑，定是非，辯治官，使百姓無怨心，安不及仁也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0110",
          "zh": "」武帝大笑曰：「善。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0111",
          "zh": "」使任安護北軍，使田仁護邊田穀於河上。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0112",
          "zh": "此兩人立名天下。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0113",
          "zh": "其後用任安為益州刺史，以田仁為丞相長史。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0114",
          "zh": "田仁上書言：「天下郡太守多為姦利，三河尤甚，臣請先刺舉三河。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0115",
          "zh": "三河太守皆內倚中貴人，與三公有親屬，無所畏憚，宜先正三河以警天下姦吏。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0116",
          "zh": "」是時河南、河內太守皆御史大夫杜父兄子弟也，河東太守石丞相子孫也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0117",
          "zh": "是時石氏九人為二千石，方盛貴。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0118",
          "zh": "田仁數上書言之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0119",
          "zh": "杜大夫及石氏使人謝，謂田少卿曰：「吾非敢有語言也，願少卿無相誣汙也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0120",
          "zh": "」仁已刺三河，三河太守皆下吏誅死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0121",
          "zh": "仁還奏事，武帝說，以仁為能不畏彊御，拜仁為丞相司直，威振天下。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0122",
          "zh": "其後逢太子有兵事，丞相自將兵，使司直主城門。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0123",
          "zh": "司直以為太子骨肉之親，父子之閒不甚欲近，去之諸陵過。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0124",
          "zh": "是時武帝在甘泉，使御史大夫暴君下責丞相「何為縱太子」，丞相對言「使司直部守城門而開太子」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0125",
          "zh": "上書以聞，請捕系司直。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0126",
          "zh": "司直下吏，誅死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0127",
          "zh": "是時任安為北軍使者護軍，太子立車北軍南門外，召任安，與節令發兵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0128",
          "zh": "安拜受節，入，閉門不出。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0129",
          "zh": "武帝聞之，以為任安為詳邪，不傅事，何也？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0130",
          "zh": "任安笞辱北軍錢官小吏，小吏上書言之，以為受太子節，言「幸與我其鮮好者」。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0131",
          "zh": "書上聞，武帝曰：「是老吏也，見兵事起，欲坐觀成敗，見勝者欲合從之，有兩心。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0132",
          "zh": "安有當死之罪甚眾，吾常活之，今懷詐，有不忠之心。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0133",
          "zh": "」下安吏，誅死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0134",
          "zh": "夫月滿則虧，物盛則衰，天地之常也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0135",
          "zh": "知進而不知退，久乘富貴，禍積為祟。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0136",
          "zh": "故范蠡之去越，辭不受官位，名傳後世，萬歲不忘，豈可及哉！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0137",
          "zh": "後進者慎戒之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "text": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}